{"tid":2358934,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"比人呃左個電話","createTime":"2021-01-08T13:15:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-09T08:37:28.000Z","uid":87154,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8ff5d789250733d191119ef31762584dd5637a0b","tid":2358934,"uid":87154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T13:15:57.000Z","msg":"見天氣凍 今日去左買衫 有個女仔sales行埋黎介紹款式<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我二話不說就拎左件上手 完全冇時間比佢同我再溝通落去<br />\n我獨特且有品味風格嚇疾左佢 令佢知難而退<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/throw.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到比錢既時候佢竟然話買多件有著數仲好抵 <br />\n唔通佢已經比我英俊既樣貌吸引迷魂癲倒哂 想我停留多陣<br />\n<br />\n好 我就揀多件 冇理由平野唔要 執輸行頭慘過敗家 <br />\n女sales眨眼之際 奔雷手拎多件又回到櫃檯前<br />\n<br />\n但佢一開口 我已經知佢仲未服氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/vampire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話買多少少差唔多個價錢有折扣 同送比你既一樣<br />\n好 想留住我 估唔到仲送埋野比我  <br />\n好 我認輸 我再揀<br />\n<br />\n最後佢冇招可以再出  <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話我已經夠分成為會員 拎我電話號碼登記 <br />\n見佢情深一片 留唔住我個心 <br />\n就唯有留低個電話號碼比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2e123332a01f86a4178da1ced75f4b089a8e9dd","tid":2358934,"uid":9392,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T13:18:59.000Z","msg":"哈哈 好有趣"},{"pid":"a2b9f6a5c1ab3086e2d45b02925a47c2a06b361a","tid":2358934,"uid":87154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2e123332a01f86a4178da1ced75f4b089a8e9dd","tid":2358934,"uid":9392,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T13:18:59.000Z","msg":"哈哈 好有趣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T13:26:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你買衫暢通無阻嗎"},{"pid":"5e2b9f9404ad6370dc78da9bcd6ad719e9ddae37","tid":2358934,"uid":382048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T13:37:30.000Z","msg":"0/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ecdd6fdc9cc8ce747f3b9fcfa7029bb25fee8ac","tid":2